        "TileImage": "$($repository fa0b9f07-d667-48d2-99c0-c5ee905fa973).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, Agent 47. \rYour targets are Oliver Fernsby, Sean Collins, and Jake Watts,  three men part of a secret Providence operation dedicated to re-educating British children. The group covertly put subliminal messages into children&apos;s books and fairy tales, successfully carrying out their task. Known for being reliable and tight-lipped, the three men quickly rose in the ranks of Providence. You will find them as part of Alexa Carlise&apos;s private staff in her Dartmoor manor. \rGood luck, 47.",
